{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kerja Magang Bukannya Disuruh Fotokopi Malah Disuruh Ngomik, Enak Banget!","content":"<p>Pernah ngga kerja magang disuruh bikin kopi atau disuruh fotokopi? Kalau pernah artinya anda kurang beruntung. Karena ada kok tempat kerja yang nerima anak magang dan ngajarin mereka cara kerja profesional. Wah, di mana tuh? Nih kita kasih tahu!</p>\n<p>Beberapa minggu yang lalu CIAYO Comics situs baca komik online Indonesia untuk pertama kalinya membuka lowongan kerja magang untuk posisi comic editor, comic scriptwriter, comic artist dan graphic designer.</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"1609\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Intern7\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1609 aligncenter\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></p>\n<p>Tentunya ini adalah kabar gembira bagi para adik-adik kelas yang baru saja menyelesaikan UTS dan UAS nya dan sedang mencari pengalaman kerja praktek di lapangan alias magang.</p>\n<p>Head of Comics Division, Beny Maulana mengatakan, “Saya tidak menyangka bahwa lamaran magang yang masuk bagus-bagus dan membludak sampai hari ini. Dikarenakan keterbatasan tempat, maka kami dipaksa untuk memilih dari sekian ratus pemagang.”</p>\n<p>“Total ada lebih dari selusin pemagang yang kami terima di gelombang ini, sebagian on-site dan sebagian remote dari luar Jakarta.”, tambah Beny.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1603\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1603\" data-attachment-id=\"1603\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Head of CIAYO Comics Comics Division, Beny Maulana\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Head of CIAYO Comics Comics Division, Beny Maulana (kanan) (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1603\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern1.jpg\" alt=\"Head of CIAYO Comics Comics Division, Beny Maulana (kanan) (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1603\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Head of CIAYO Comics Comics Division, Beny Maulana (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div>\n<p>Hari Senin yang lalu (27/03/2017) para pemagang hadir untuk briefing di kantor CIAYO Comics, tepatnya di The Dragon Building, Mangga Dua Square, Jakarta Utara.</p>\n<p>Briefing dipimpin langsung oleh Founder &amp; CEO dari CIAYO Corp, Borton Liew.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1608\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1608\" data-attachment-id=\"1608\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"CEO CIAYO Corp, Borton Liew (kiri)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;CEO CIAYO Corp, Borton Liew (kiri) (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern6.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-1608 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern6.jpg\" alt=\"Founder dan CEO CIAYO Corp, Borton Liew (kiri) (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1608\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Founder dan CEO CIAYO Corp, Borton Liew (kiri) (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div>\n<p>Di briefing ini Borton menegaskan bahwa, “Di CIAYO Comics kalian dijamin akan mendapatkan pengalaman bekerja di industri komik yang sebenarnya. Selain dapat bekerjasama membantu para author dan komikus format webtoon yang memang ahli di bidangnya, kamu akan dituntun untuk membuat komik sendiri. Jika komikmu bagus, saya tidak akan berpikir dua kali untuk mempublikasikannya di CIAYO Comics.”</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1604\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1604\" data-attachment-id=\"1604\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Borton Liew Melihat Portfolio Pemagang\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Borton Liew Melihat Portfolio Pemagang (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1604\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern2.jpg\" alt=\"Borton Liew Melihat Portfolio Pemagang (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1604\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton Liew Melihat Portfolio Pemagang (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Seorang calon pemagang sempat bertanya apakah mereka akan disuruh bikin kopi di CIAYO Comics. Jawab Borton, “Haha yang pasti saya sendiri bisa menjamin jika kalian disini tidak akan disuruh bikin kopi atau nongkrong di mesin fotokopi. Kalian harus mendapatkan sesuatu ketika kerja magang disini.”</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1607\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1607\" data-attachment-id=\"1607\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Perkenalan Calon Magang\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Perkenalan Calon Magang (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1607\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern5.jpg\" alt=\"Perkenalan Calon Magang (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1607\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Perkenalan Calon Magang (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div>\n<p>Tambahnya, “Alasan kenapa kami membuka magang ini yaitu selain kalian bisa belajar dari kami, kami juga bisa belajar dari kalian. Karena kita semua juga masih belajar.”</p>\n<p>Borton sendiri yang adalah seorang comic writer dari komik <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/fourger\">Fourger Inc</a> sempat memberikan sedikit arahan bagaimana membuat premis, plot, sinopsis dan karakter dari sebuah cerita.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1605\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1605\" data-attachment-id=\"1605\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Borton Liew dan Beny Maulana Memberikan Tips Membuat Komik Digital\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Borton Liew dan Beny Maulana Memberikan Tips Membuat Komik Digital (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1605\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern3.jpg\" alt=\"Borton Liew dan Beny Maulana Memberikan Tips Membuat Komik Digital (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton Liew dan Beny Maulana Memberikan Tips Membuat Komik Digital (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Para pemagang dapat dengan bebas menyesuaikan dengan jadwal kuliahnya untuk magang di CIAYO Comics. Ada yang masuk seminggu sekali, seminggu dua kali, dan ada juga yang mau masuk setiap hari.</p>\n<p>Borton juga menambahkan bahwa tidak tertutup kemungkinan bagi para pemagang yang memiliki performa yang bagus selama kerja magang akan dikontrak sebagai kontributor atau pekerja penuh waktu di CIAYO Comics.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1606\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1606\" data-attachment-id=\"1606\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-magang-bukannya-disuruh-fotokopi-malah-disuruh-ngomik-enak-banget/attachment/intern4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Borton Liew sedang Membaca Resume Pemagang\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Borton Liew sedang Membaca Resume Pemagang (CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1606\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern4.jpg\" alt=\"Borton Liew sedang Membaca Resume Pemagang (CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Intern4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1606\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton Liew sedang Membaca Resume Pemagang (CIAYO Pictures)</p></div>\n<p>Wah asyik yah! Nice…</p>\n<p>Jadi gimana dong bagi adik-adik kita yang lain yang belum berkesempatan untuk melamar magang?</p>\n<p>Ketika kami menanyakan hal ini kepada Beny, beliau memberikan secercah harapan, “Ya coba aja dikirim dulu portfolionya ke <a href=\"mailto:join@ciayo.com\">join@ciayo.com</a> siapa tahu anda sedang beruntung.”</p>\n<p>So tunggu apalagi? Bagikan saja info ini ke adik-adik kelasnya yang sedang membutuhkan magang. Kapan lagi bisa magang di perusahaan komik sekece ini!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"9c7d8f31-77f8-511c-9765-c9d9b0b73ee1"}}}